select  case when   exists(
select * from ( SELECT xn,
                                          xq,
                                          kcdm,
                                          xh,
                                          zzzscj,
                                          ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY kcdm, xh ORDER BY xn desc, xq desc, zzzscj desc) AS rn
                                     FROM t_cj_xscjb
                                    where kcdm = #{p_kcdm_cxrw_zckc} 
                                      and xh = #{xkxg_xsOne.xh}) where rn!=1 and zzzscj>=60) then 'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_XDCSYDSXBKXD' else '1' end from dual ;
 select distinct
    CASE 
        WHEN  (select   a.zzcj end from   (select jbyydm,xh,max(zzcj)zzcj from     T_KS_SLJKSCJB group by jbyydm,xh )   a where a.xh = #{xkxg_xsOne.xh} and a.jbyydm=b.jbyydm   ) >=b.KSCJYQ
            THEN '1'
        ELSE 'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_KCWYDJBFHBKXD'
    END AS result from t_rw_rwapb b where id= #{ p_rwid} and KSCJYQ is not null 
;
 select case when #{p_rwid} is null then '1' else
   (  
  case when (select count(1) from t_rw_rwap_kxkxsmd    where rwid=#{p_rwid} ) > 0 then 
  nvl ((select distinct '1'  from t_rw_rwapb where xn=#{p_xn}and xq=#{p_xq} and kcdm = #{rwOne.kcdm} and 
 id in(
 select rwid from t_rw_rwap_kxkxsmd  where xh = #{p_xh})),'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_BFHKXMDBKXD' ) else '1' end ) end sxz   from dual 
;
